Package com.company.ems.builder

Class PartTimeEmployeeBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.company.ems.builder.PartTimeEmployeeBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
EmployeeBuilder
public class PartTimeEmployeeBuilder extends Object implements EmployeeBuilder
Concrete builder class for constructing part-time employees.

The PartTimeEmployeeBuilder is responsible for creating and assembling a PartTimeEmployee object, one attribute at a time, using the builder pattern. This class implements the EmployeeBuilder interface, defining how each attribute is set for a part-time employee.

Once all the attributes have been set, the build() method is called to return the fully constructed PartTimeEmployee.
